變身的時候，什麼感覺？

579
01:10:28,570 --> 01:10:31,150
Remember those experiments we volunteered for at Harvard?
記得我們在哈佛的時候 自願參加的那些試驗嗎？

580
01:10:31,230 --> 01:10:33,320
Those induced hallucinations?
誘發幻覺試驗？

581
01:10:34,070 --> 01:10:37,490
It's a lot like that,just a thousand times amplified.
很像那個，只不過放大了一千倍

582
01:10:39,330 --> 01:10:43,250
