我的腦子裏就像被倒入了一升的酸

583
01:10:43,330 --> 01:10:48,170
-Do you remember anything? -Just fragments. Images.
- 還記得什麼嗎？  - 一些碎片，圖像

584
01:10:48,670 --> 01:10:51,840
There's too much noise.I can never derive anything out of it.
干擾太多，實在記不起什麼了

585
01:10:51,920 --> 01:10:55,510
-But then it's still you inside it. -No. No, it's not.
- 但那終歸是你  - 不，不是了

586
01:10:57,930 --> 01:11:02,100
I don't know.In the cave, I really felt like it knew me.
我不知道，在洞穴的時候 我真的感覺它認識我

587
01:11:02,850 --> 01:11:04,270
Maybe your mind is in there,
也許你的心還在那裏

588
01:11:04,350 --> 01:11:06,980
it's just overcharged and can't process what's happening.
只是過載了，無法正常處理形勢了

589
01:11:07,060 --> 01:11:10,360
I don't want to control it.I want to get rid of it.
我不想控制它，我想擺脫它

590
01:11:23,580 --> 01:11:25,040
Are you ready?
準備好了嗎？

591
01:11:25,120 --> 01:11:26,870
Let's even the playing field a little.
讓我們把戰鬥變得更公平些

592
01:11:30,290 --> 01:11:31,590
Gentlemen.
先生們

593
01:11:34,420 --> 01:11:35,470
(HORN BLARING)

594
01:11:35,550 --> 01:11:39,220
