Me in a metal tube, deep underground,
你讓我在世上最擁擠的城市和數百人一起

601
01:12:31,480 --> 01:12:33,940
with hundreds of people in the most aggressive city in the world?
擠在地下的鐵罐子裏？

602
01:12:34,020 --> 01:12:36,690
Right. Let's get a cab.
好吧，打車

603
01:12:36,780 --> 01:12:40,990
CAB DRlVER: Come on, now! Let's go!You're too slow! You drive like a woman!
上路啦！你們開得這麼慢，跟娘們似的！

604
01:12:41,410 --> 01:12:43,700
(HIP-HOP MUSIC PLAYING ON RADIO)

605
01:12:45,910 --> 01:12:47,500
-Very nice. You see her? -Oh, my.
- 真漂亮，看到她的表情沒？  - 噢天

606
01:12:47,580 --> 01:12:50,710
Very pretty. Watch out, you goat!
很好，小心，白癡！

607
01:12:50,790 --> 01:12:52,830
Breathe, breathe, breathe.
呼吸，呼吸

608
01:12:56,130 --> 01:12:58,800
Are you out of your mind?
你瘋了嗎？

609
01:12:58,880 --> 01:13:00,220
-What is wrong with you? -What's the matter, baby?
- 你怎麼了？  - 怎麼了，寶貝？

610
01:13:00,300 --> 01:13:02,010
