612
01:13:03,850 --> 01:13:05,100
Asshole!
混蛋！

613
01:13:06,350 --> 01:13:07,810
(BETTY GRUNTS)

614
01:13:08,230 --> 01:13:10,730
You know, I know a few techniques could help you
我知道一些技巧，可以幫你有效的

615
01:13:10,810 --> 01:13:15,020
-manage that anger very effectively. -You zip it. We're walking.
- 控制怒氣  - 閉嘴，走路

616
01:13:15,440 --> 01:13:16,480
Okay.
好吧

617
01:13:24,030 --> 01:13:25,990
Excuse me. Dr Sterns?
打擾了，史登博士？

618
01:13:26,080 --> 01:13:28,620
-Yes. -I'm sorry to bother you. I'm Elizabeth Ross.
- 是我  - 不好意思打擾了，我是伊麗莎白·羅斯

619
01:13:29,540 --> 01:13:31,540
Oh! Dr Ross!
哦！羅斯博士！

620
01:13:31,620 --> 01:13:34,540
-I have someone who'd like to meet you. -Okay.
- 我想為您引見一個人  - 好

621
01:13:37,050 --> 01:13:38,510
It's Mr Blue, isn't it?
藍先生，是你嗎？

622
01:13:40,340 --> 01:13:41,720
Mr Green?
綠先生？

623
01:13:43,970 --> 01:13:47,640
I got to tell you,I've been wondering if you were even real.
告訴你，我曾經都懷疑你的存在

624
01:13:47,720 --> 01:13:49,470
And if you were, what would it look like?
我想如果你不是虛擬的，那會是什麼樣？

625
01:13:49,560 --> 01:13:54,230
A person with that much power lurking in him.
身上潛伏著那麼巨大的能量

626
01:13:54,310 --> 01:13:55,940
Nothing could have surprised me more
想不到真的能在現實中和你握手

627
01:13:56,020 --> 01:13:58,900
than this unassuming man shaking my hand.
這真是太讓人太驚喜了

628
01:13:58,980 --> 01:14:01,650
But, look. We're not strolling into the park for a picnic, here.
不過我們可不是要過家家

629
01:14:01,740 --> 01:14:03,410
Even if everything goes perfectly,
即使一切順利

630
01:14:03,490 --> 01:14:07,330
if we induce an episode,if we get the dosage exactly right,
即使我們能讓你變身，而且控制好劑量

631
01:14:08,330 --> 01:14:10,250
is that going to be a lasting cure
但那會是持久有效的治癒

632
01:14:10,330 --> 01:14:13,670
or just some antidote to suppress that specific flare-up?
還是只是暫時的抑制呢？

633
01:14:15,960 --> 01:14:17,420
I don't know.
不得而知了

634
01:14:18,170 --> 01:14:22,880
What I'm saying is that if we overshoot this by even the smallest integer
我的意思是，即使多出這麼一點點劑量

635
01:14:23,840 --> 01:14:28,720
we're dealing with concentrations with extraordinary levels of toxicity.
那裏面濃縮的也是多得驚人的毒素

636
01:14:28,810 --> 01:14:33,350
-You mean it could kill him. -Kill him? Yeah. I should say so.
- 你是說會害死他  - 害死他？對，是這個意思

637
01:14:35,060 --> 01:14:37,190
You should know that there's a flip side to this, too.
還有另一種情況

638
01:14:37,270 --> 01:14:40,820
If we miss on the low side,if we induce me and it fails,
如果劑量少了 如果我變身了而治療又失敗了

639
01:14:40,900 --> 01:14:43,360
this will be very dangerous for you.
那你可就危險了

640
01:14:45,160 --> 01:14:49,200
Look. I've always been more curious than cautious,
聽著，我行事一向以好奇心驅使多過謹慎

641
01:14:49,280 --> 01:14:53,540
and that's served me pretty well.So, are we going to do this?
不過到目前為止還沒出過什麼事 那我們到底做不做試驗？

642
01:15:48,590 --> 01:15:50,220
How you feeling, man?
感覺如何，夥計？

643
01:15:51,970 --> 01:15:53,560
Like a monster.
像野獸一樣

644
01:16:13,450 --> 01:16:15,200
Okay. On the table.
好吧，上桌子

645
01:16:15,950 --> 01:16:21,340
These will protect you from yourself if you have a strong reaction.
如果反應劇烈，這些能就你

646
01:16:22,590 --> 01:16:25,550
You can tell me later if you thought it was strong.
你可以事後再告訴我反應是否劇烈

647
01:16:29,760 --> 01:16:34,180
Oh, come on! Stupid graduate students.
噢，不是吧！那幫白癡研究生

648
01:16:38,810 --> 01:16:39,940
Okay...
好的…

649
01:16:40,520 --> 01:16:41,980
You, you, you.
這個，這個，還有這個

650
01:16:43,610 --> 01:16:47,070
This will be a somewhat novel sensation.
這將會是從未有過的奇妙體驗

651
01:16:47,900 --> 01:16:49,660
(MACHINE STARTING UP)

652
01:16:49,740 --> 01:16:51,240
We have begun.
開始了

653
01:16:53,080 --> 01:16:56,120
The dialysis machine will mix the antidote with your blood.
透析機會把解毒藥和你的血液混合

654
01:16:56,200 --> 01:17:00,670
Except the antidote will only take hold once we've achieved a full reaction.
只不過解毒藥要等到完全反應時 才能加入

655
01:17:00,750 --> 01:17:01,920
Just relax.
放鬆吧

656
01:17:02,670 --> 01:17:06,000
Okay. We are comprehensive.
好了，進入狀態了

657
01:17:09,220 --> 01:17:10,680
Here you go.
這個給你

658
01:17:20,690 --> 01:17:22,690
All right. We set to pop?
好了，準備好了嗎？

659
01:17:25,190 --> 01:17:27,360
I'd take your hands off him.
換我就不會抓他手

660
01:17:42,210 --> 01:17:43,540
(GRUNTING)

661
01:17:47,170 --> 01:17:49,210
Oh, my God!
噢天！

662
01:17:56,810 --> 01:17:58,140
(GRUNTING)

663
01:17:59,470 --> 01:18:01,520
(SCREAMING)

664
01:18:03,310 --> 01:18:05,360
Wait, wait! There's more! Wait!
等等！還有！等等！

665
01:18:16,160 --> 01:18:18,740
-Now. Okay, now! -STERNS: Wait.
- 現在可以了，快！  - 等等

666
01:18:18,830 --> 01:18:21,410
Now, do it! Do it!
趕緊！快點！

667
01:18:28,920 --> 01:18:31,420
Bruce! Bruce, look at me.
布魯斯！布魯斯，看著我

668
01:18:31,510 --> 01:18:36,010
Stay with me. The antidote, now!Sterns, do it now!
挺住，趕緊加解毒藥！史登，快點！

669
01:18:37,470 --> 01:18:41,480
Bruce, look at me. Look in my eyes.Please, look in my eyes.
布魯斯，看著我，看著我的眼睛 求你了，看著我的眼睛

670
01:18:41,560 --> 01:18:42,600
(MACHINE BEEPING)

671
01:18:42,680 --> 01:18:45,100
Oh, you've got to be kidding me!
開玩笑吧！

672
01:18:54,490 --> 01:18:56,070
(HULK GROANING)

673
01:19:04,710 --> 01:19:05,920
Bruce.
布魯斯

674
01:19:06,000 --> 01:19:07,380
Oh, my God.
噢天

675
01:19:18,760 --> 01:19:21,770
Bruce? Bruce, can you hear me?
布魯斯？布魯斯，能聽到我說話嗎？

676
01:19:25,810 --> 01:19:26,980
Bruce?
布魯斯？

677
01:19:27,810 --> 01:19:29,020
(GASPS)

678
01:19:35,820 --> 01:19:39,200
It's okay. You're okay. You're okay.
沒事了，沒事了

679
01:19:42,620 --> 01:19:44,000
You did it.
你挺過來了

680
01:19:44,160 --> 01:19:46,830
He's fine. This is fantastic.
他沒事了，太奇妙了

681
01:19:46,920 --> 01:19:48,250
BETTY: It's over.
結束了

682
01:19:49,170 --> 01:19:50,250
Hi.
嗨

683
01:19:50,590 --> 01:19:51,710
Hi.
嗨

684
01:20:00,050 --> 01:20:06,020
That was the most extraordinary thing I have seen in my entire life!
這是我這輩子見過的最不可思議的情景！

685
01:20:06,100 --> 01:20:07,690
Okay, you know what? Stop, please.
你消停一下吧，求你了

686
01:20:07,770 --> 01:20:10,150
We need to go back and talk about what just happened in there.
我們得談談剛才發生的事

687
01:20:10,230 --> 01:20:14,030
Absolutely. Okay. The gamma pulse came from the amygdala.
顯然伽瑪脈衝來自扁桃腺

688
01:20:14,110 --> 01:20:15,860
-I think Dr Ross's primer... -Are you okay?
- 我想羅斯博士的核酸合成引物… - 你還好吧？

689
01:20:15,940 --> 01:20:19,200
...lets the cells absorb the energy temporarily, and then it abates.
使得細胞暫時吸收了能量，然後又減弱

690
01:20:19,280 --> 01:20:22,080
That's why you didn't die of radiation sickness years ago!
這就是你數年前沒有死於輻射的原因！

691
01:20:22,160 --> 01:20:24,870
Now, maybe we've neutralised those cells permanently,
現在，也許我們已經永久的 幹掉這些細胞了

692
01:20:24,950 --> 01:20:26,870
or maybe we just suppressed that event.
但也許只是暫時抑制住了

693
01:20:26,960 --> 01:20:29,290
I'm inclined to think the latter,but it's hard to know
我傾向於後者，但目前還不好說

694
01:20:29,370 --> 01:20:31,170
because none of our test subjects ever survived.
因為我們的試驗樣本都沒有生還

695
01:20:31,250 --> 01:20:32,880
-Of course, they weren't getting the primer! -Wait, wait.
- 當然了，因為它們沒有核酸合成引物… - 等等

696
01:20:32,960 --> 01:20:34,380
-Wait, what did you just say? -They weren't getting
- 等等，你剛才說什麼？ - 他們沒有

697
01:20:34,460 --> 01:20:37,010
-the myostatin primer... -No, no, no. Test subjects?
- 肌肉抑制素核酸合成引物 - 不是，試驗樣本？

698
01:20:38,050 --> 01:20:39,800
What test subjects?
什麼試驗樣本？

699
01:20:40,510 --> 01:20:41,550
Come with me.
跟我來

700
01:20:58,650 --> 01:21:02,570
-SPARR: What's the activity level? -Snipers are covering Alpha sector.
- 情況如何？ - 狙擊手已經能覆蓋A區了

701
01:21:03,410 --> 01:21:04,830
STERNS ON RADIO.;We started on rats and mice,
我們從小白鼠下手

702
01:21:04,910 --> 01:21:07,500
but it just compIeteIy fried them,so we had to go bigger.
不過試驗一開始它們就被烤焦了 所以我們得找大點的動物

703
01:21:07,750 --> 01:21:10,870
And we still don't know which is more toxic,the gamma or your blood.
我們還不清楚，伽瑪和你的血液 哪個更具毒性

704
01:21:10,960 --> 01:21:14,710
-What do you mean, my blood? -Bruce, this is all you.
- 我的血液？什麼意思？ - 布魯斯，這些都是你的

705
01:21:15,550 --> 01:21:19,550
You didn't send me much to work with,so I had to concentrate it and make more.
你沒給我寄太多，所以我只好通過濃縮 製造更多樣本

706
01:21:19,630 --> 01:21:22,890
With a little more trial and error,there's no end to what we can do!
通過試錯法，這個試驗將潛力無窮

707
01:21:22,970 --> 01:21:26,680
This is potentially Olympian!
多麼偉大的工程！

708
01:21:26,770 --> 01:21:30,270
This gamma technology has limitless applications.
伽瑪技術的應用前景很廣

709
01:21:30,350 --> 01:21:32,400
We'll unlock hundreds of cures.
數百種治病方法將誕生

710
01:21:32,480 --> 01:21:35,610
We will make humans impervious to disease!
人類從此將免受疾病困擾！

711
01:21:49,790 --> 01:21:51,460
No, no, we've got to destroy it.
不行，我們得毀了它們

712
01:21:51,920 --> 01:21:53,790
-Wait, what? -All of it.
- 等等，什麼？ - 全部

713
01:21:53,920 --> 01:21:55,290
Tonight. We're gonna incinerate it.
今晚我們就得把它們都毀了

714
01:21:55,380 --> 01:21:57,630
-Is this the whole supply? -What...
- 這是總開關？ - 等等…

715
01:21:57,710 --> 01:21:59,260
We could get the Nobel for this!
我們可以因此得到諾貝爾！

716
01:21:59,340 --> 01:22:01,550
You don't understand the power of this thing.
你不明白這東西的威力

717
01:22:01,630 --> 01:22:04,260
It is too dangerous. It cannot be controlled.
這太危險了，我們無法控制

718
01:22:04,930 --> 01:22:06,430
At your discretion, shooter.
狙擊手，自行掌握開槍時機

719
01:22:06,510 --> 01:22:07,970
STERNS ON RADIO.; ...three of us!This is Promethean fire!
…我們三個！這是普羅米修斯之火啊（意為將開創生物學新時代）

720
01:22:08,060 --> 01:22:09,100
BRUCE ON RADIO.; It's just...
但是…

721
01:22:09,180 --> 01:22:10,430
SOLDIER ON RADIO.; No shot.
無法瞄準

722
01:22:13,770 --> 01:22:15,560
Blonsky's going in.
布朗斯基進去了

723
01:22:17,770 --> 01:22:20,650
GENERAL.; Blonsky, stand down.My daughter's in there!
布朗斯基，別衝動，我女兒在裏面！

724
01:22:23,240 --> 01:22:24,320
We have the antidote now.
我們已經有解毒藥了

725
01:22:24,410 --> 01:22:27,240
They don't want the antidote!They want to make it a weapon!
他們要的不是解毒藥！他們想製造武器！

726
01:22:29,330 --> 01:22:30,950
(SIRENS WAlLING)

727
01:22:34,120 --> 01:22:36,130
