這事會變得一發不可收拾

728
01:22:36,340 --> 01:22:38,380
You don't know how powerful this thing is.
你不知道這東西的威力

729
01:22:38,460 --> 01:22:40,460
I hate the government just as much as anyone,
我和別人一樣痛恨政府

730
01:22:40,550 --> 01:22:42,340
but you're being a little paranoid,don't you think?
但你不覺得自己有點偏執了？

731
01:22:46,260 --> 01:22:47,470
(GASPS)

732
01:22:50,140 --> 01:22:51,640
Bruce! Bruce!
布魯斯！布魯斯！

733
01:22:53,350 --> 01:22:54,600
Get out.
出去

